# 🤖 Multi-Source AI Knowledge Assistant

An AI-powered Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) application that allows users to ask questions from multiple knowledge sources including **PDFs, DOCX files, TXT files, Websites, and YouTube videos**.

Built using **LangChain**, **Groq LLM**, **HuggingFace Embeddings**, **ChromaDB**, and **Streamlit**.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📄 Upload PDF documents
- 📝 Upload DOCX documents
- 📃 Upload TXT files
- 🌐 Extract knowledge from websites
- 🎥 Extract transcripts from YouTube videos
- 💬 Ask questions in natural language
- 🧠 Conversational memory for follow-up questions
- ⚡ Fast inference using Groq LLM
- 📚 Source-based answers using RAG
- 🎨 Clean and interactive Streamlit UI

---

# 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| Python | Programming Language |
| Streamlit | User Interface |
| LangChain | RAG Pipeline |
| Groq | Large Language Model |
| HuggingFace | Embeddings |
| ChromaDB | Vector Database |
| youtube-transcript-api | YouTube Transcript Extraction |
| BeautifulSoup | Website Parsing |

